MIPS: cevt-r4k: Use CAUSEF_TI, CAUSEF_PCI constants

Use CAUSEF_TI and CAUSEF_PCI constants from asm/mipsregs.h rather than
the magic values (1 << 30) and (1 << 26).

Signed-off-by: James Hogan <james.hogan@imgtec.com>
